title: HOUR 3- Albert Breer Oct 07, 2020
itunes:title: HOUR 3- Albert Breer Oct 07, 2020
description:
Albert Breer tells Dan that it is going to be hard for the Titans to be ready to play a live game with missing so much practice time. Albert explains how the Titans health could affect the Chiefs and the Buffalo Bills game later on the schedule which could be for first place.
